race.comment: EARN TO BURN (3) was gelded before his return to the track last start and the change was there for all to see, dominating a BM68 over this distance at the Sunshine Coast. Meets a deeper field this time but another run like the last one might be good enough. GET READY LASS (4) opened this prep with two impressive efforts then struggled in the $3 million Sunlight over 1100m at the Gold Coast last time. At her best over 1000m and back in this company she looks a key runner. BLITZBURG (1) hasn't landed a blow in his two runs this prep, the latest a modest effort in the Sunlight. Gets a host of gear changes today and will strip fitter so he might be worth one more chance. Classy filly SUNRAYS (2) is back from a 21-week spell. The winner of five from seven including two at Listed level. Cejay Graham has won three from three aboard this exciting three-year-old. Ticks all the boxes.
